Day 94 – Road to Fluent Spanish Summary
Today focused on Pimsleur Unit 3 Lesson 10, continuing this week’s new conversational phrase set, reviewing new Duolingo and Memrise vocabulary, and practicing spontaneous conversation without notes. The emphasis was on strengthening past tense usage, engagement/travel vocabulary, and making this week’s new Medellín phrases feel more natural.

